<----- TAILWIND CSS SETUP IN REACT PROJECT ----->
1. first create react project by npm create vite@latest ---> setup proejct ---> cd: project_name
2. npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer ---> npm install -D tailwindcss@3.4.17
3. npx tailwindcss init -p ---> it will create a file names tailwind.confi.js u just have to copy paste this code:

/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
export default {
  content: [
    "./index.html",
    "./src/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx}",
  ],
  theme: {
    extend: {},
  },
  plugins: [],
}

4. in project dr ---> src ---> index.css ---> paste this :

@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

5. then npm run dev and u r ready to go


